1 Capitol Arts and Grounds Commission, shall approve:
2 (i) The artist selected to design the bust;
3 (ii) The final design of the bust; and
4 (iii) The exact location of the bust.
5 (C) The Secretary of State may accept gifts, grants, and
6 donations from individuals and organizations to be deposited as trust funds
7 into the Maurice Lee "Footsie" Britt Memorial Bust Fund.
